Governor Godwin Obaseki of Edo State on Wednesday rolled out the bulldozer to bring down thw hotel bulding belonging to Tony Adun, alias Kabaka.
It was gathered tbat the government had to vacate the injunction secured   by Kabaka estraining the Edo State Government from executing the demolition notice earlier served him with regards to his illegally-sited property in Ugbor-Amagba axis of Benin City, the Edo State Government on Wednesday rolled out  heavy duty equipment and security officials to the property for its demolition.

Details of the demolition exercise later.





			
